title: The One Where Bob and Monet Contemplate Their Existence
description:
This week Bob and Monet sit down together to talk TikTok trends, rap battles, and existentialism. From viral sounds to alien life to tour buzz, Bob and Monet bring us along for the stream of consciousness ride of a lifetime!
See Monét and Bob on tour this fall by going to bobandmonet.com !!
Want to see exclusive Sibling Rivalry Bonus Content? Head over to www.patreon.com/siblingrivalrypodcast to be the first to see our latest Sibling Rivalry Podcast Videos!
